                            <i class="ph ph-check"></i>
                            There are many variations of passage of lorem.
                        </li>
                        <li class="position-relative fw-bold">
                            <i class="ph ph-check"></i>
                            Available but the majority alteration.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="d-sm-flex align-items-center">
                        <a href="private-flights.html" class="default-btn">
                            Discover More
                            <i class="ph ph-arrow-right"></i>
                        </a>
                        <div class="call-info d-flex align-items-center">
                            <div class="icon">
                                <i class="ph-fill ph-phone-call"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="info">
                                <span class="d-block">
                                    CALL ANYTIME
                                </span>
                                <a href="tel:+9288006780" class="fw-bold">
                                    +92 23456778
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="shape1">
        <img src="~/User/images/shapes/shape1.png" alt="shape1">
    </div>
